    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://chicago.craigslist.org/nch/fbh/6040838463.html"></div>
        </div>
Currently seeking full and part time cashiers for closing and weekend shifts at Ohare Airport.  Some mid shifts available but mainly closing and weekends. Seeking friendly, motivated people serious about working. Must be punctual, thorough and a team player. Must have stability in work history but will consider first time job seekers. We have a fun atmosphere, are very busy and have a good group of core employees. Must be able to pass an airport background check and be available asap. $10.50-$11 to start. <br>
<br>
COOKS\LINE PERSONNEL:<br>
Seeking someone with flat grill, short order cook experience. Stable work history, able to work weekends and closing shifts (10pm we close), fast paced environment and able to work in a team environment. Looking for someone who is punctual, good attendance, has pride in their work and able to start asap...Cook pay is $11-$13 an hour to start....Line Personnel is a good job for someone that assembled sandwiches at Subway, McDonalds or looking for that first job....We promote from within when opportunities come up. Please submit your resume or work history and the position you are applying for. We are doing interviews this week.    </section>

<ul class="notices">
            <li>Principals only. Recruiters, please don't contact this job poster.</li>
            <li>do NOT contact us with unsolicited services or offers</li>
</ul>

